# _Ju … des_

- _Ju pli longe, des pli bone._ – the longer the better

# _Ajn_

- _kiom ajn_ – however much

# The Prefix _dis-_

denotes separation, dispersal:

- ___dis__ĵeti_ – to scatter
- ___dis__sendi_ – to broadcast

# The Suffix _-on_

denotes a fraction:

- _du__on__o_   – half
- _tri__on__o_  – third
- _kvar__on__o_ – quarter
- _ses__on__o_  – sixth
